file.name: googleapis.com-resourceviews-v1beta2-swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  contact:
    name: Google
    url: https://google.com
  description: The Resource View API allows users to create and manage logical sets of
    Google Compute Engine instances.
  license:
    name: Creative Commons Attribution 3.0
    url: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
  termsOfService: https://developers.google.com/terms/
  title: Google Compute Engine Instance Groups
  version: v1beta2
  x-apiClientRegistration:
    url: https://console.developers.google.com
  x-apisguru-categories:
    - backend
  x-logo:
    url: https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/2x/googlelogo_color_272x92dp.png
  x-origin:
    - converter:
        url: https://github.com/lucybot/api-spec-converter
        version: 2.6.0
      format: google
      url: https://www.googleapis.com/discovery/v1/apis/resourceviews/v1beta2/rest
      version: v1
  x-preferred: true
  x-providerName: googleapis.com
  x-serviceName: resourceviews
externalDocs:
  url: https://developers.google.com/compute/
tags:

  - name: zoneViews
paths:
  "/{project}/zones/{zone}/operations":
    get:
      description: Retrieves the list of operation resources contained within the specified
        zone.
      operationId: resourceviews.zoneOperations.list
      parameters:
        - description: Optional. Filter expression for filtering listed resources.
          in: query
          name: filter
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Optional. Maximum count of results to be returned. Maximum value is
            500 and default value is 500.
          in: query
          name: maxResults
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 0
            maximum: 500
            default: 500
        - description: Optional. Tag returned by a previous list request truncated by
            maxResults. Used to continue a previous list request.
          in: query
          name: pageToken
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Name of the project scoping this request.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Name of the zone scoping this request.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/OperationList"
      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute.readonly
          Oauth2c:

        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman.readonly
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman.readonly
      tags:
        - zoneOperations
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/alt"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
  "/{project}/zones/{zone}/operations/{operation}":
    get:
      description: Retrieves the specified zone-specific operation resource.
      operationId: resourceviews.zoneOperations.get
      parameters:
        - description: Name of the operation resource to return.
          in: path
          name: operation
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Name of the project scoping this request.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Name of the zone scoping this request.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:

      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only

        - Oauth2:

        - Oauth2:

          Oauth2c:

        - Oauth2:

    parameters:

      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
  "/{project}/zones/{zone}/resourceViews":
    get:
      description: List resource views.
      operationId: resourceviews.zoneViews.list
      parameters:
        - description: "Maximum count of results to be returned. Acceptable values are 0 to
            5000, inclusive. (Default: 5000)"
          in: query
          name: maxResults
          schema:

            minimum: 0
            maximum: 5000
            default: 5000

            token can be used to request the next page of results from a
            previous list request.
          in: query
          name: pageToken
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The project name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The zone name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:

          description: Successful response

                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ZoneViewsList"
      security:
        - Oauth2:

          Oauth2c:

        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute.readonly
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute.readonly
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman.readonly
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman.readonly
      tags:
        - zoneViews
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/alt"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"

      operationId: resourceviews.zoneViews.insert
      parameters:

          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:

        - description: The zone name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:

      responses:

      security:

          Oauth2c:

        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:

        - Oauth2:

        - Oauth2:

        - Oauth2:

      operationId: resourceviews.zoneViews.get
      parameters:
        - description: The project name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:

        - description: The name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: resourceView
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The zone name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true

            type: string
      responses:

          description: Successful response
          content:

          Oauth2c:

        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute.readonly
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute.readonly
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman.readonly
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman.readonly

    parameters:

      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
  "/{project}/zones/{zone}/resourceViews/{resourceView}/addResources":
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/alt"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
    post:
      description: Add resources to the view.
      operationId: resourceviews.zoneViews.addResources
      parameters:
        - description: The project name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: resourceView
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The zone name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:

      responses:

          description: Successful response
          content:

          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
      tags:
        - zoneViews
  "/{project}/zones/{zone}/resourceViews/{resourceView}/getService":
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/alt"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
    post:
      description: Get the service information of a resource view or a resource.
      operationId: resourceviews.zoneViews.getService
      parameters:
        - description: The project name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The name of the resource if user wants to get the service
            information of the resource.
          in: query
          name: resourceName
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: resourceView
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The zone name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ZoneViewsGetServiceResponse"
      security:
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:

        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
      tags:

  "/{project}/zones/{zone}/resourceViews/{resourceView}/removeResources":
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/alt"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
    post:
      description: Remove resources from the view.
      operationId: resourceviews.zoneViews.removeResources
      parameters:
        - description: The project name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: resourceView
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The zone name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/ZoneViewsRemoveResourcesRequest"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Operation"
      security:
        - Oauth2:

          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
      tags:
        - zoneViews
  "/{project}/zones/{zone}/resourceViews/{resourceView}/resources":
    get:
      description: List the resources of the resource view.
      operationId: resourceviews.zoneViews.listResources
      parameters:
        - description: The requested format of the return value. It can be URL or URL_PORT.
            A JSON object will be included in the response based on the format.
            The default format is NONE, which results in no JSON in the
            response.
          in: query
          name: format
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - NONE
              - URL
              - URL_PORT
        - description: The state of the instance to list. By default, it lists all
            instances.
          in: query
          name: listState
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - ALL
              - RUNNING
            default: ALL
        - description: "Maximum count of results to be returned. Acceptable values are 0 to
            5000, inclusive. (Default: 5000)"
          in: query
          name: maxResults
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 0
            maximum: 5000
            default: 5000
        - description: Specifies a nextPageToken returned by a previous list request. This
            token can be used to request the next page of results from a
            previous list request.
          in: query
          name: pageToken
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The project name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: resourceView
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The service name to return in the response. It is optional and if it
            is not set, all the service end points will be returned.
          in: query
          name: serviceName
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The zone name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:

          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ZoneViewsListResourcesResponse"
      security:
        - Oauth2:

          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute.readonly
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute.readonly
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman
        - Oauth2:

          Oauth2c:

      tags:

    parameters:

      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
  "/{project}/zones/{zone}/resourceViews/{resourceView}/setService":
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/alt"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/fields"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/key"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/oauth_token"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/prettyPrint"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/quotaUser"
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/userIp"
    post:
      description: Update the service information of a resource view or a resource.
      operationId: resourceviews.zoneViews.setService
      parameters:
        - description: The project name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: project
          required: true

            type: string
        - description: The name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: resourceView
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: The zone name of the resource view.
          in: path
          name: zone
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/ZoneViewsSetServiceRequest"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful response
          content:
            "*/*":
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Operation"
      security:
        - Oauth2:

          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform
        - Oauth2:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
          Oauth2c:
            - https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute
        - Oauth2:

          Oauth2c:

servers:
  - url: https://www.googleapis.com/resourceviews/v1beta2/projects
components:
  parameters:
    alt:
      description: Data format for the response.
      in: query
      name: alt
      schema:
        type: string
        enum:
          - json
        default: json
    fields:
      description: Selector specifying which fields to include in a partial response.
      in: query
      name: fields
      schema:
        type: string
    key:
      description: API key. Your API key identifies your project and provides you with API
        access, quota, and reports. Required unless you provide an OAuth 2.0
        token.
      in: query
      name: key
      schema:
        type: string
    oauth_token:
      description: OAuth 2.0 token for the current user.
      in: query
      name: oauth_token
      schema:
        type: string
    prettyPrint:
      description: Returns response with indentations and line breaks.
      in: query
      name: prettyPrint
      schema:
        type: boolean
        default: true
    quotaUser:
      description: Available to use for quota purposes for server-side applications. Can be
        any arbitrary string assigned to a user, but should not exceed 40
        characters. Overrides userIp if both are provided.
      in: query
      name: quotaUser
      schema:
        type: string
    userIp:
      description: IP address of the site where the request originates. Use this if you
        want to enforce per-user limits.
      in: query
      name: userIp
      schema:
        type: string
  securitySchemes:
    Oauth2:
      description: Oauth 2.0 implicit authentication
      type: oauth2
      flows:
        implicit:
          authorizationUrl: https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/auth
          scopes:
            https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform: View and manage your data across Google Cloud Platform services
            https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform.read-only: View your data across Google Cloud Platform services
            https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute: View and manage your Google Compute Engine resources
            https://www.googleapis.com/auth/compute.readonly: View your Google Compute Engine resources
            https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman: View and manage your Google Cloud Platform management resources
              and deployment status information
            https://www.googleapis.com/auth/ndev.cloudman.readonly: View your Google Cloud Platform management resources and
              deployment status information
    Oauth2c:
